### Phase 4 — Full Role Permission Matrix
### Tests every role against every endpoint category.
### Run 00_get_tokens.http first.
###
### Legend: ✓ = should return 2xx | ✗ = should return 403

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# RESOURCE: /api/fhir-resource/{tab}  (Settings/non-patient endpoints)
# Requires: SCOPE_user/Patient.read
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ADMIN → GET /fhir-resource/patients → EXPECT 200 ✓
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}

###

### PROVIDER → GET /fhir-resource/patients → EXPECT 200 ✓
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token_provider}}

###

### NURSE → GET /fhir-resource/patients → EXPECT 200 ✓
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token_nurse}}

###

### MA → GET /fhir-resource/patients → EXPECT 200 ✓
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token_ma}}

###

### FRONT_DESK → GET /fhir-resource/patients → EXPECT 200 ✓
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token_frontdesk}}

###

### BILLING → GET /fhir-resource/patients → EXPECT 200 ✓
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token_billing}}

###

### PATIENT → GET /fhir-resource/patients → EXPECT 403 ✗ (only has patient/* scopes)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{token_patient}}

###

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# RESOURCE: POST /api/fhir-resource/{tab}/patient/{id}
# Requires: SCOPE_user/Patient.write
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ADMIN → POST /fhir-resource/observations/patient/1 → EXPECT 201 ✓
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/observations/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"resourceType":"Observation","status":"final"}

###

### PROVIDER → POST /fhir-resource/observations/patient/1 → EXPECT 201 ✓
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/observations/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_provider}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"resourceType":"Observation","status":"final"}

###

### NURSE → POST /fhir-resource/observations/patient/1 → EXPECT 201 ✓
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/observations/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_nurse}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"resourceType":"Observation","status":"final"}

###

### MA → POST /fhir-resource/observations/patient/1 → EXPECT 403 ✗ (no Patient.write)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/observations/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_ma}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"resourceType":"Observation","status":"final"}

###

### FRONT_DESK → POST /fhir-resource/observations/patient/1 → EXPECT 201 ✓ (has Patient.write)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/observations/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_frontdesk}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"resourceType":"Observation","status":"final"}

###

### BILLING → POST /fhir-resource/observations/patient/1 → EXPECT 403 ✗ (no Patient.write)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/observations/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_billing}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"resourceType":"Observation","status":"final"}

###

### PATIENT → POST /fhir-resource/observations/patient/1 → EXPECT 403 ✗
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/observations/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_patient}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"resourceType":"Observation","status":"final"}

