# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SCOPE ISOLATION: Cross-scope leakage checks
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### BILLING (has Claim.read/write) CANNOT access admin endpoints
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token_billing}}
# EXPECT: 403

###

### NURSE (has clinical write) CANNOT access admin users
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token_nurse}}
# EXPECT: 403

###

### FRONT_DESK (has Patient.write) CANNOT submit claims
### This would need a specific billing endpoint — adjust path as needed
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/fhir-resource/claims
Authorization: Bearer {{token_frontdesk}}
# EXPECT: 403 (FRONT_DESK has no Claim.read scope)

###
